HOW WE DISCIPLINE THE BOYS,

471
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:05,300
WHAT CAR WE BUY, EVERYTHING.
I CONSULT YOU.

472
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,800
OH, SURE, AND IF YOU DISAGREE,
YOU IGNORE ME.

473
00:25:07,900 --> 00:25:09,800
