474
00:25:09,900 --> 00:25:12,400
BASICALLY,
I CHECK MY BALLS AT THE DOOR,

475
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,900
AND THAT'S FINE. IT WORKS.

476
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:17,100
