WHEN YOU WALK THROUGH <i>THAT</i> DOOR,

477
00:25:17,100 --> 00:25:19,700
YOU GOTTA CHECK YOURS.

478
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:26,400
OKAY.

479
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:27,900
REALLY?

480
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:30,600
REALLY.

481
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:33,700
