485
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:45,200
I DON'T CARE IF YOU <i>THINK</i>
YOU KNOW WHAT'S BEST!

486
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:46,900
YOU DON'T! I DO,

487
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:49,900
BECAUSE I'M THE BOSS,
AND WHAT I SAY GOES.

488
00:25:49,900 --> 00:25:51,000
(whispers) YEAH, THAT'S IT.
GIVE IT TO ME.

489
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:53,000
SO WHEN I MAKE A DECISION,
IT STAYS MADE!

490
00:25:53,100 --> 00:25:55,400
YOU GOT THAT, LYNETTE?
(normal voice) YES, SIR.

491
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:59,000
(whispers)
OKAY, THAT'S ENOUGH.
(whispers) NO, JUST ONE MORE.

492
00:25:59,100 --> 00:26:02,000
(normal voice) AND IF I WANT
YOUR OPINION, I'LL ASK FOR IT!

493
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:04,900
BUT I PROBAB WON'T, BECAUSE
I'M THE BOSS! ARE WE CLEAR?

494
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:07,000
SERIOUSLY,
STOP OR I WILL HURT YOU.

495
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:09,500
OKAY, I'VE MADE MY POINT.

496
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:12,700
ANYBODY NEEDS ME, I'LL BE
IN THE BACK DRINKING A BEER.

497
00:26:27,300 --> 00:26:30,400
MMM. THIS IS DELICIOUS.

498
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,900
DON'T GET TOO FULL.

499
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:34,500
