504
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:45,900
NO.

505
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:47,400
OH! YOU'RE FLIRTING.
YEAH.

506
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:49,600
(laughs) OKAY. DO IT AGAIN.
I SWEAR I'LL GET IT.

507
00:26:49,700 --> 00:26:52,800
(chuckles) IT'S OKAY.
DO YOU WANT SOME COFFEE?

508
00:26:52,900 --> 00:26:56,400
YOU BET I WANT COFFEE...
NICE AND HOT AND--

509
00:26:56,400 --> 00:27:00,200
JUST FINISH YOUR SOUP,
AND WE'LL GET NAKED.

510
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:07,500
SORRY TO BOTHER YOU,
MRS. SOLIS.

511
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:10,400
I WORK WITH LUKE.
IS HE AVAILABLE?

512
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:12,900
CHARLES?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

513
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:15,600
